{"tid":450382,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(樂器)古時啲人點數拍子？","createTime":"2017-10-28T06:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T03:33:22.000Z","uid":93395,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5176c22c7fd7ffa95f930cb9756d298570d48bdc","tid":450382,"uid":93395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"又無拍子機<br />\n<br />\n點練拍子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩樂器會唔會越彈越快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁樣睇樂譜又點知要彈幾快<br />\n<br />\n拍band個beat又係咪亂鳩咁黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/70086_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fcontent%2Fphoto%2Fv1%2F70086_WM.jpg&h=9203ff44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db231911706d21b3a0a1b19069d71324f43db7ec","tid":450382,"uid":55511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"beatbox (9估"},{"pid":"fbe87b8f636bcbd683bbba4ac6da7517ad809030","tid":450382,"uid":50744,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"稟夫人 小人原本住在蘇州嘅城邊"},{"pid":"be378af6ac4e2f23fc4a783cbada5a4fa75d58dc","tid":450382,"uid":33190,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"中國以前係冇正式樂譜，靠口傳心授<br />\n靠feel，如果冇人識就真係失傳<br />\n<br />\n講樂感同記憶，所以有時彈出黎唔同都唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬個話，拍子機係機械嘢，一早就有<br />\n而且tempo 係跟時間，有鐘有時間觀念就會數到架la"},{"pid":"e4c3bfe80c2253f7680b42f6b107b8aaf6aab718","tid":450382,"uid":93395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>稟夫人 小人原本住在蘇州嘅城邊</blockquote><br />\n家中有屋又有田 生活樂無邊"},{"pid":"60b863ceb23c710db1aa4f55bcb660c669780e4f","tid":450382,"uid":24641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:39:26.000Z","msg":"將軍令"},{"pid":"0e4eae88e3526ae46bcd16f1228f46dda975b7bf","tid":450382,"uid":93395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:48:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國以前係冇正式樂譜，靠口傳心授<br />\n靠feel，如果冇人識就真係失傳<br />\n<br />\n講樂感同記憶，所以有時彈出黎唔同都唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬個話，拍子機係機械嘢，一早就有<br />\n而且tempo 係跟時間，有鐘有時間觀念就會數到架la</blockquote><br />\n咁啲歌咪姐係靠背？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n傳得幾多個又有幾多人夠料再傳下一個"},{"pid":"5798cc13ede923d996270abb8629125e55b505d0","tid":450382,"uid":33190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:51:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中國以前係冇正式樂譜，靠口傳心授<br />\n靠feel，如果冇人識就真係失傳<br />\n<br />\n講樂感同記憶，所以有時彈出黎唔同都唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬個話，拍子機係機械嘢，一早就有<br />\n而且tempo 係跟時間，有鐘有時間觀念就會數到架la</blockquote><br />\n咁啲歌咪姐係靠背？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n傳得幾多個又有幾多人夠料再傳下一個</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔係冇，不過佢唔係好似現代樂譜咁<br />\n係淨係記音，你睇完之後，都要聽一次先會識彈"},{"pid":"dff98164c98d636a7f30720918a038e7bd28ae2f","tid":450382,"uid":143250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:19:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國以前係冇正式樂譜，靠口傳心授<br />\n靠feel，如果冇人識就真係失傳<br />\n<br />\n講樂感同記憶，所以有時彈出黎唔同都唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬個話，拍子機係機械嘢，一早就有<br />\n而且tempo 係跟時間，有鐘有時間觀念就會數到架la</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平行時空<br />\n咁減字譜係咩黎？古琴真係毒撚到冇人識？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家搵到最早嘅譜好似係唐宋年間 <br />\n齋記載但搵唔到真證嘅就係話周秦漢就有"},{"pid":"a18875a72ec055c4531cc74f5cec501f2faf3047","tid":450382,"uid":143250,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:23:33.000Z","msg":"高山流水相傳作於先秦 分拆於唐 成為高山同流水二曲<br />\n現時古琴比較多人知嘅係流水 高山都有 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/151955_5587ceb58263f39178efd24e0d632a04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F151955_5587ceb58263f39178efd24e0d632a04.jpg&h=1e804a03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/151959_88f2d8d8e86e31eda7c11300921c2966.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F151959_88f2d8d8e86e31eda7c11300921c2966.jpg&h=137e888f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n音樂黎講我諗中國應該係世界數一數二最早出現<br />\n周代禮樂個樂就係指音樂 其時已經有古琴<br />\n去到唐宋文化興起 都開始出現減字譜<br />\n印象中晉代都有本"},{"pid":"8708494190471e4fbee890331dabccd28f34020b","tid":450382,"uid":143250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:24:28.000Z","msg":"而家學古琴都仲係減字譜 另以簡譜相輔"},{"pid":"7501e5aed16f26820af24fb77918c09cfa39400e","tid":450382,"uid":57447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:28:35.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"220bd3d6c4f0e6e5bdc02c252f4ceb1d51570689","tid":450382,"uid":93395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高山流水相傳作於先秦 分拆於唐 成為高山同流水二曲<br />\n現時古琴比較多人知嘅係流水 高山都有 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/151955_5587ceb58263f39178efd24e0d632a04.jpg https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/151959_88f2d8d8e86e31eda7c11300921c2966.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F151955_5587ceb58263f39178efd24e0d632a04.jpg%20https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F151959_88f2d8d8e86e31eda7c11300921c2966.jpg&h=fd82e052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n音樂黎講我諗中國應該係世界數一數二最早出現<br />\n周代禮樂個樂就係指音樂 其時已經有古琴<br />\n去到唐宋文化興起 都開始出現減字譜<br />\n印象中晉代都有本</blockquote><br />\n見到都有80,70bpm呢啲<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣都分到拍子？<br />\n<br />\n我見到啲符號都同西方嗰啲都不謀而合<br />\n<br />\n係近代combine翻嘅？"},{"pid":"c7943c51cd028130f5b32bc7697bc1454210ee1b","tid":450382,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高山流水相傳作於先秦 分拆於唐 成為高山同流水二曲<br />\n現時古琴比較多人知嘅係流水 高山都有 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/151955_5587ceb58263f39178efd24e0d632a04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F151955_5587ceb58263f39178efd24e0d632a04.jpg&h=1e804a03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/151959_88f2d8d8e86e31eda7c11300921c2966.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F151959_88f2d8d8e86e31eda7c11300921c2966.jpg&h=137e888f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n音樂黎講我諗中國應該係世界數一數二最早出現<br />\n周代禮樂個樂就係指音樂 其時已經有古琴<br />\n去到唐宋文化興起 都開始出現減字譜<br />\n印象中晉代都有本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中樂冇研究開，西方既就玩過幾樣，所以唔係好認識減字譜<br />\n<br />\n但減字譜會記低你個速度，幾多拍咁樣架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為中國古樂譜淨係最多識叫你到某個位停一停，慢一慢咁"},{"pid":"eed38f73fd43d5f0de4290794afc24d4dbb263b8","tid":450382,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:49:51.000Z","msg":"指揮同打鼓都係要用心來數"},{"pid":"5fd0b491ed252d620f99e5b4fd45c69193370f5a","tid":450382,"uid":143250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>高山流水相傳作於先秦 分拆於唐 成為高山同流水二曲<br />\n現時古琴比較多人知嘅係流水 高山都有 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/151955_5587ceb58263f39178efd24e0d632a04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F151955_5587ceb58263f39178efd24e0d632a04.jpg&h=1e804a03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/151959_88f2d8d8e86e31eda7c11300921c2966.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F151959_88f2d8d8e86e31eda7c11300921c2966.jpg&h=137e888f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n音樂黎講我諗中國應該係世界數一數二最早出現<br />\n周代禮樂個樂就係指音樂 其時已經有古琴<br />\n去到唐宋文化興起 都開始出現減字譜<br />\n印象中晉代都有本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中樂冇研究開，西方既就玩過幾樣，所以唔係好認識減字譜<br />\n<br />\n但減字譜會記低你個速度，幾多拍咁樣架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為中國古樂譜淨係最多識叫你到某個位停一停，慢一慢咁</blockquote><br />\n呢個係整合咗簡譜嘅減字譜 原本果啲係就咁全文字<br />\n包曬音同速度"},{"pid":"616bac092852c68b87d31faf0a9d63405308112f","tid":450382,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:07:05.000Z","msg":"管弦樂團個指揮都冇拍子機聽住嚟指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdaf8d87454434c9005c5e0f7a3882f25e6b59c2","tid":450382,"uid":93395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>管弦樂團個指揮都冇拍子機聽住嚟指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地有聽住個beat練過幾千萬次<br />\n<br />\n但古時嘅人無得聽黎練喎"},{"pid":"73b148859494f9633bbac27fabca063736a3652a","tid":450382,"uid":143250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T08:16:00.000Z","msg":"呢個係琴之界收錄o既唐代減字譜<br />\n《碣石調幽蘭》(相傳係孔子作)<br />\n撰刊年代 唐 大歷年間(762-779)<br />\n撰辑人 丘明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/161038_6f093887dc903ae9b4bba116f8f31d86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F161038_6f093887dc903ae9b4bba116f8f31d86.jpg&h=7e50877c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/161038_1671097d89ee604b2a64f642483c097f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F161038_1671097d89ee604b2a64f642483c097f.jpg&h=58e809bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你問我入面講緊乜 坦白講睇唔明<br />\n但碣石調幽蘭至今仍存在<br />\n音、拍子就係跟返古代o既減字譜重編而成"},{"pid":"24d0b6efd46f1e01076ae00b3eb4e243dafdb6db","tid":450382,"uid":143250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T13:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bd3c2fec63ae61ad5c146dd4334e21178349e2","tid":450382,"uid":55585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"古時都係用生果<br />\n蘋果 士多啤梨 蘋果 橙"},{"pid":"b3b35d4d23f778577752eda1f619dbfd077aa081","tid":450382,"uid":143250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古時都係用生果<br />\n蘋果 士多啤梨 蘋果 橙</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}